---
const repo = "https://github.com/GeneralD/Magia";
const wiki = "https://github.com/GeneralD/Magia/wiki";
const tip = "0x222222222C769bEcDdb7829B763e9F31F06B2d42";
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-line py-12">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <span class="grid h-8 w-8 place-items-center rounded-lg border border-line-strong bg-surface font-display text-lg font-extrabold text-gradient">M</span>
          <span class="font-display text-lg font-bold tracking-wide">MAGIA</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-sm text-sm text-muted">
          プロのための NFT ジェネレーター。<br />究極のカスタマイズ性と処理速度を。
        </p>
      </div>

      <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-sm text-muted">
        <a class="transition-colors hover:text-ink" href="#features">機能</a>
        <a class="transition-colors hover:text-ink" href="#how">仕組み</a>
        <a class="transition-colors hover:text-ink" href="#showcase">実績</a>
        <a class="transition-colors hover:text-ink" href={repo} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        <a class="transition-colors hover:text-ink" href={wiki} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Wiki</a>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-3 border-t border-line pt-6 text-xs text-faint sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
      <p>&copy; {year} GeneralD · Magia. 自己の責任でご自由にご利用ください。</p>
      <p class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span>投げ銭</span>
        <code class="rounded bg-surface px-2 py-1 font-mono text-[11px] text-muted">{tip}</code>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
